1
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,440
[Palms on Love]

2
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:09,810
[Adapted from the online novel,
The Age of Wind and Rain]

3
00:00:09,810 --> 00:00:14,780
[Episode 4]

4
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:31,560
Nan.

5
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:33,680
Find out all the information

6
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:36,680
about Mrs. Yun Lian
from the past five years.

7
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:38,600
All of it.

8
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:41,440
Got it?

9
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:42,360
Yes.

10
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:12,600
Hello?

11
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,520
Pin.

12
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,080
She has gone out.

13
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,520
When she arrives,

14
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,800
I'll see you at the old spot.

15
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,120
Okay.

16
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,640
How come you're back?

17
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:34,720
I'm a bit tired.

18
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,320
Need to get some rest.

19
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,200
Okay.

20
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,440
Rest well.

21
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:40,880
Hold on.

22
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:42,760
What's the matter?

23
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,160
Medicine?

24
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,360
For me?

25
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,440
Thank you.

26
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,280
Don't just stand there.

27
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,320
Take the medicine.

28
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,480
Got it.

29
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,600
Get out of here

30
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:07,400
after you're healed.

31
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,160
I'll take it later.

32
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:10,560
I'm busy right now.

33
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,480
Take it now.

34
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,000
Who knows if you will avoid recovery
on purpose

35
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,560
to stay?

36
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,280
Happy?

37
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,240
Thank you.

38
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,280
Ji Lianyun.

39
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,440
You are a maid now.

40
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,400
What's your hurry to get out?

41
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,120
I've been trying to tolerate

42
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:47,720
and help you.

43
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,960
If you leave now,

44
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,800
I will never help you again.

45
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,880
You better not.

46
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,360
Tonight is my inauguration ceremony.

47
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:14,760
Do you know

48
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,680
why I allowed you to stay?

49
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,960
I want you to watch me

50
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,000
become the military governor.

51
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:42,740
[Shanghai Xinxin Hotel]

52
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,560
Come on, Mr. Xue.

53
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,400
Can I change it?

54
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,160
Come on.

55
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,280
I want it.

56
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,080
It's mine.

57
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,080
You're so generous.

58
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:04,560
Mr. Xue, I took a fancy to a necklace.

59
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,120
Mr. Xue.

60
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,040
Mr. Xue, have another drink.

61
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,840
Alright.

62
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,440
Great.

63
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,360
Buy more.

64
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,240
Okay.

65
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,240
Tell me what you want.

66
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,360
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

67
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,560
That's very kind of you.

68
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,800
All of you, leave.

69
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,800
Come and sit.

70
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,040
Come on.

71
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,440
Don't be petty.

72
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,960
Take a look.

73
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,160
It's just a photo.

74
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,240
Your man is already dead.

75
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,880
Relax.

76
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,480
Keep your cool.

77
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,640
What?

78
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,040
I've been keeping my cool
for five years.

79
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,480
You know what?

80
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,040
Over the past five years,

81
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,040
I've been living in fear

82
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,800
all the time.

83
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,200
It's all because of you.

84
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:34,440
Xue Zhihai.

85
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,480
Don't be afraid.

86
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,760
You'll be my wife
once I become the governor.

87
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,560
Governor?

88
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:43,240
Didn't you say
that once the old man died,

89
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,640
you would be the governor?

90
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:47,200
How come Xue Dongfeng took his position?

91
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,240
He's just an acting governor.

92
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,320
Just you wait and see.

93
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,400
You just don't know how to be gentle.

94
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:06,240
I can't attend the ceremony
with bruises.

95
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:16,760
I'll take care of the photo.

96
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,640
As for the ceremony,

97
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,200
the livelier, the better.

98
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,600
Don't try to fool me.

99
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:26,360
When have I ever done that?

100
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,200
It's him.

101
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,040
Yes.

102
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,080
I told you before.

103
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,320
Hello, Mr. Wang.

104
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,040
You look well today.

105
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,720
You must fix it for me.

106
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,080
Mr. Xue is young and promising.

107
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:46,280
We're all here for Governor Xue.

108
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,000
Sir, have you seen Pin?

109
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,240
No, I haven't.

110
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,040
Couldn't find her.

111
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,360
She should have been singing on stage.

112
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,200
Governor Xue is so young.

113
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:58,080
Mrs. Yun Lian is quite attractive.

114
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:04,080
I'll take my leave first.

115
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:07,040
- See you later.
- Later.

116
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,360
Come on.

117
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,480
Let's drink.

118
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,200
I'll show you around.

119
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,720
That's all.

120
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,160
Anyway, it's not true.

121
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,400
It seems so.

122
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,600
Yeah.

123
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,880
Mr. Yang's business...

124
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,120
Be careful.

125
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,840
Ms. Yun Lian.

126
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,720
You don't remember me?

127
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,240
I am Fang Changlin,

128
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,160
Fang Fei's nephew.

129
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,800
Mr. Fang.

130
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,160
Yes.

131
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:38,960
I remember you.

132
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,080
Why is she here?

133
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,840
Mr. Xue.

134
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,240
Governor Xue.

135
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:44,600
I have things to do.

136
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,520
I gotta go.

137
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,680
Wait.

138
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,600
We're family.

139
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,440
What can I do for you?

140
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,520
Have a drink with me.

141
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,840
Waiter.

142
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,880
Hello.

143
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,400
Drink.

144
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,160
I've drunk it.

145
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,720
I'm really busy.

146
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,680
I must go.

147
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,040
What?

148
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,640
Did I let you go?

149
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,560
I haven't finished yet.

150
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,120
Tell me what you're up to.

151
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:22,760
I can help.

152
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,520
Congrats, Governor Xue.

153
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,600
Thanks.

154
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,800
I can cheer you up.

155
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,280
Became a governor

156
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,080
at such a young age.

157
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,200
Lower your voice.

158
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,280
No rush.

159
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:38,440
Since you don't chat,

160
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,680
let's drink.

161
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,360
Drink.

162
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,680
You studied abroad.

163
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,560
If you leave now,

164
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:50,440
I will never help you again.

165
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,040
Drink.

166
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,440
Watch your manners.

167
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,000
It's Governor Xue's big day.

168
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,560
Who do you think you are?

169
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,360
As a lowly maid, it's your honor

170
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,760
to drink with me.

171
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,840
I don't care what occasion it is.

172
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,640
No matter what happens,

173
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,840
you have to drink.

174
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,480
You wench.

175
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,520
Do you have a death wish?

176
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,560
What is he doing with that gun?

177
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,800
He drew his gun.

178
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,640
Stop!

179
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,840
Fang Changlin.

180
00:09:54,770 --> 00:09:58,460
♪I'm waiting for the rain
to wet the city♪

181
00:09:58,550 --> 00:10:01,660
♪At dusk♪

182
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:06,220
♪As I ran into someone I missed
at the street corner♪

183
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:09,740
♪Old memories flashed♪

184
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:13,340
♪If I can shout that I miss you♪

185
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:17,340
♪I'll be waiting for the sunshine
in the rain♪

186
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:23,940
♪If your heart is as cold as ice♪

187
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:28,980
♪My heart will call for you♪

188
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:32,780
♪Are you as resolute as I am♪

189
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:36,740
♪You wake me up to see you♪

190
00:10:36,860 --> 00:10:39,980
♪I'm sure your heart will be soft♪

191
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:43,610
♪You approach me in the name of love♪

192
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:47,780
♪As time goes by, I realize
there's no time like the present♪

193
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:52,860
♪I have no regrets when being with you♪

194
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:55,500
♪And you're like the rising wind♪

195
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:59,060
♪I ask you not to leave me
in the name of love♪

196
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:03,980
♪Wind blows and we part ways in silence♪

197
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:06,220
♪And you're like the cloud♪

198
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:10,770
♪Moving closer or farther away from me♪
